# SQL Migration Conventions

See `architecture-data.mdc` for full data layer rules.

## Structure
- Location: `database/migrations/`
- Name: `NNN_descriptive_name.sql` (e.g. `093_project_expense_vouchers.sql`)
- Idempotent where possible: `IF NOT EXISTS`, `IF EXISTS`
- Do not drop columns/tables without explicit plan and backup

## Multi-Tenant
- All business tables need `tenant_id`; index `(tenant_id, …)` for scoped queries
- PostgreSQL migrations are the sole source of truth — do not add SQLite schema for new columns
